\n<br />\n加拿大司法部門目前仍在審理是否向美國引渡孟晚舟。孟晚舟被捕10天後即獲得取保候審。今年5月，孟晚舟一度認為可能立即獲釋回國的希望落空，只得繼續等候引渡裁決。<br />\n<br />\n兩名加拿大人18個月來則一直處於被關押狀態。加拿大政府此前曾指控中國當局對兩人實行&ldquo;任意關押&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n美國司法當局指控孟晚舟在華為集團下屬集團在伊朗的業務中對銀行隱瞞資訊，違反美國對伊朗的經濟制裁。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T23:13:03.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍 2020"},{"pid":"54b06527633241f60f17d2dcab0780cb2eb7469f","tid":2071432,"uid":187676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb80e4ded71f4958b231981b36c5308650f50e4","tid":2071432,"uid":78971,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T22:18:52.000Z","msg":"快啲判埋刑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈做你愈冇得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"已經翻唔到轉頭"},{"pid":"11b5c8f9fd3ac7298a33e44685bbaf55c5653e94","tid":2071432,"uid":124439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"54b06527633241f60f17d2dcab0780cb2eb7469f","tid":2071432,"uid":187676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb80e4ded71f4958b231981b36c5308650f50e4","tid":2071432,"uid":78971,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T22:18:52.000Z","msg":"快啲判埋刑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愈做你愈冇得返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T23:18:46.000Z","msg":"已經翻唔到轉頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T23:49:41.000Z","msg":"一條直路 4面8方都有刀手 最好既解決方法就係加速沖出去"},{"pid":"ae197a203036ef2351eabb8a715470f526938a44","tid":2071432,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T23:59:45.000Z","msg":"判刑，快"},{"pid":"0a43e965c8488f4e418de07512b877f78f33d11d","tid":2071432,"uid":70336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T00:25:25.000Z","msg":"突然諗起<br />\n賭仔去澳門賭場玩<br />\n輸到百佳 重瘋狂加注<br />\n最後當然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" 